      Press release
    </span>
  <h1 class="gem-c-title__text gem-c-title__text--long">
    Annual Clinical Excellence Awards 2021 competition launches
  </h1>
</div>
  </div>
  
  <div class="govuk-grid-column-two-thirds">
    
  <p class="gem-c-lead-paragraph">As of Monday 7 December high-performing consultant doctors and dentists, and academic GPs can apply for the annual national awards. </p>

  </div>
</div>

